Reverse your friend's name
Your friend wants to see the pronunciation of his/ her name when it gets reversed. Help him/ her to find the reversed string using program.

Input (stdin)
Naveen Kumar

Output (stdout)
ramuK neevaN

Input (stdin)
valentina

Output (stdout)
anitnelav

Input (stdin)
Rose chris

Output (stdout)
sirhc esoR

PROGRAM IN CPP

#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() 
{
  string name;
  getline(cin,name);
  for(string::reverse_iterator i = name.rbegin();i<name.rend();i++)
  	cout<< *i;
  return 0;
}


